FBIS4-37463 "drnes119_l_94010" FBIS-NES-94-119 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 ISRAEL Peres Urges All To Act `Properly' in Lebanon Peres Urges All To Act `Properly' in Lebanon TA2106053594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 21 Jun 94 TA2106053594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el English BFN [Text] Reacting to the escalation of fighting in south Lebanon, Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres called on all parties, including Syria, to try and stabilize the situation. He was speaking to No'omi Segal at a reception in Jerusalem. [Begin Peres recording] Well, it happened before we started the negotiations. From time to time there were confrontations in Lebanon. It is not an entirely new phenomenon. But I hope that the responsible parties will act properly, including the Syrian party, to stop it. [end recording]
